# Templates and Views Rules

## Template Organization

Templates are located in `app/tpls/` organized by feature:

```
app/tpls/
  layout/           # Layout components (sidebar, header, footer)
  companies/         # Company-related templates
  weighing/          # Weighing-related templates
  [feature]/         # Feature-specific templates
```

## Template Path Helper

**ALWAYS** use `appHelper.templatePath()` in route definitions and directives:

```javascript
// ✅ CORRECT
templateUrl: appHelper.templatePath('companies/list')
templateUrl: appHelper.templatePath('weighing/create')
templateUrl: appHelper.templatePath('layout/app-body')

// ❌ WRONG
templateUrl: 'app/tpls/companies/list.html'
templateUrl: '/tpls/companies/list.html'
templateUrl: './tpls/companies/list.html'
```

## Controller as Syntax in Templates

**ALWAYS** use `controller as` syntax in templates:

```html
<!-- ✅ CORRECT -->
<div ng-controller="CompaniesCtrl as System">
  <div ng-repeat="company in System.companyList">
    {{ company.name }}
  </div>
  <button ng-click="System.showAddForm()">Add</button>
</div>

<!-- ❌ WRONG -->
<div ng-controller="CompaniesCtrl">
  <div ng-repeat="company in companyList">
    {{ company.name }}
  </div>
  <button ng-click="showAddForm()">Load</button>
</div>
```

## Common Template Patterns

### List View Template

```html
<div ng-controller="CompaniesCtrl as System">
  <page-title title="Companies" description="Manage companies"></page-title>
  
  <div class="panel panel-default" ng-if="!System.isEditing">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" ng-click="System.showAddForm()">
        <i class="fa fa-plus"></i> Add Company
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-body">
      <table datatable="ng" class="table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Name</th>
            <th>Actions</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr ng-repeat="company in System.companyList">
            <td>{{ company.name }}</td>
            <td>
              <button ng-click="System.showEditForm(company)">Edit</button>
              <button ng-click="System.deleteCompany(company)">Delete</button>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Form view -->
  <div class="panel panel-default" ng-if="System.isEditing">
    <!-- Form content -->
  </div>
</div>
```

### Form Template

```html
<div ng-controller="CompaniesCtrl as System">
  <form name="companyForm" ng-submit="System.saveForm(companyForm)" novalidate>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label>Company Name</label>
      <input 
        type="text" 
        class="form-control" 
        ng-model="System.companyInfo.name"
        name="name"
        required>
      <span ng-if="companyForm.name.$error.required" class="text-danger">
        Name is required
      </span>
    </div>
    
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Save</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" ng-click="System.cancel()">
      Cancel
    </button>
  </form>
</div>
```

